name: Octoproto Genesis // 00
description:
Dear ladies and jelly spoons. I come before you to stand behind you to tell you something I know nothing about. This Friday, which is a good Saturday, there is a women’s meeting just for men. Admission is free, pay at the door, pull up a chair and sit on the floor. This world is either real, and you are reading this now, or it has been written out, at this exact moment, for your eyes only. Read, but don’t think too hard, because they might be trying to tell you something. This reality is what you make it. Shine on.
